)]\"><nav class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-4\"><div class=\"space-y-1\"><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🏠</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">首页</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">概览与推荐</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/skill\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">✨</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Skill</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">可复用的能力模块</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/mcp\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🔌</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">MCP</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">外部工具与服务接入</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/agent\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🤖</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Agent</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">自主决策的AI助手</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/prompt\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">📝</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Prompt</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">高效沟通的模板</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/workflow\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🔄</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Workflow</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">多步骤任务编排</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/knowledge\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🗃️</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Knowledge</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">企业知识智能检索</div></div></a></div></nav><div class=\"shrink-0 p-4 border-t border-gray-100 bg-white\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400\"><div>版本 v1.0.0</div><div class=\"mt-1\">© 2026 AI Tools Center</div></div></div></aside><main class=\"flex-1 ml-72\"><div class=\"p-8\"><nav class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6\"><a class=\"hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/learn\">学院</a><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><a class=\"hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/learn/path/beginner\">入门路径</a><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-gray-900 font-medium\">MCP 协议</span></nav><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-rose-500 to-red-500 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\"><span class=\"text-4xl\"></span><div><h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold\">MCP 协议</h1><p class=\"text-white/80\">连接 AI 与真实世界</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 text-white/80 text-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg><span>预计 <!-- -->65分钟</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg><span>入门路径</span></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-4 mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm\"><span class=\"text-gray-500\">难度选择：</span><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-blue-600 text-white\" href=\"/learn/mcp/beginner\">入门路径</a><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-200\" href=\"/learn/mcp/developer\">开发者路径</a><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-200\" href=\"/learn/mcp/architect\">架构师路径</a></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-8\"><div class=\"prose prose-gray max-w-none\"><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-rose-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">1</span>第一课：MCP 是什么？</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-rose-50 border-l-4 border-rose-500 p-4 rounded-r-lg\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">核心认知</h3><p class=\"text-gray-700\"><strong>MCP（Model Context Protocol）</strong>是让 AI 模型能够安全、规范地访问外部工具和数据源的<strong>标准化协议</strong>。</p></div><div class=\"bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-bold mb-3\">类比理解：给 AI 安装&quot;感觉器官&quot;</h4><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-gray-700\">没有 MCP 的 AI</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">被困在&quot;云端&quot;的超级大脑，无法访问实时数据或执行具体操作</p></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-rose-700\">有 MCP 的 AI</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">安装了&quot;感觉器官&quot;和&quot;操作臂&quot;，能实时联网、读取文件、调用 API</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-3 text-green-700\">核心价值</h4><ul class=\"text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1\"><li>• <strong>标准化</strong>：统一的协议，任何工具都能快速接入</li><li>• <strong>安全性</strong>：标准化的权限控制和数据隔离</li><li>• <strong>可扩展</strong>：社区生态丰富，海量 Server 可选</li><li>• <strong>跨平台</strong>：支持桌面端、Web、服务器等</li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-rose-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">2</span>第二课：MCP 架构</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">MCP 生态的三个核心组件：</h4><div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-4\"><div class=\"p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg text-center\"><div class=\"text-3xl mb-2\"></div><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">Host（宿主）</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">运行 AI 应用的环境<br/>Claude Desktop / 自定义 Web App</p></div><div class=\"p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-lg text-center\"><div class=\"text-3xl mb-2\"></div><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">Client（客户端）</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">运行在 Host 中<br/>负责与 Server 通信</p></div><div class=\"p-4 bg-purple-50 rounded-lg text-center\"><div class=\"text-3xl mb-2\"></div><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">Server（服务器）</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">提供 API 或数据源<br/>独立进程运行</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg font-mono text-sm\"><pre>用户请求\n    ↓\nHost (Claude Desktop)\n    ↓\nClient (MCP Client)\n    ↓ ←→ STDIO/HTTP 通信\nServer (文件系统/数据库/API)\n    ↓\n返回结果给用户</pre></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-rose-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">3</span>第三课：MCP 能做什么？</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"p-3 border-l-4 border-blue-500 bg-gray-50 rounded-r-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-1\">文件系统访问</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">读取/写入本地文件，执行命令行</p></div><div class=\"p-3 border-l-4 border-green-500 bg-gray-50 rounded-r-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-1\">数据库查询</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">SQL 查询、数据检索</p></div><div class=\"p-3 border-l-4 border-purple-500 bg-gray-50 rounded-r-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-1\">API 调用</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">REST/GraphQL 集成</p></div><div class=\"p-3 border-l-4 border-orange-500 bg-gray-50 rounded-r-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-1\">SaaS 集成</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Notion, Slack, GitHub 等</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/learn/path/beginner\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M15 19l-7-7 7-7\"></path></svg>返回<!-- -->入门路径</a><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/learn\">返回学院<svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main></div></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0j6kpnbwgrhei.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[30824,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"Providers\\\"]\\n3:I[87161,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5q